</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d355n1-ptr" id="PJA11d355n1">1</a>

   <p>See <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> to F. &amp; A. Dubbeldemuts, 21 June, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-11-02-0281&amp;expandNote=PJA11d338n2#PJA11d338n2" class="document">note 2</a>, above.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d355n2-ptr" id="PJA11d355n2">2</a>

   <p>No reply by <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> has been found, nor is there evidence that he did anything regarding the proposal to convert the sum due on the pending bills of exchange into a loan.</p>

